name: Astrals #4 "In Trio"
description:
The fourth work of the four audiovisual work series titled "Astrals".

Astrals series consists of four audiovisual compositions that were inspired by the subtle existence of cosmos and all within. 

This fourth piece was the unification of all the three individual astral that exist within this series which could also act as the addition toward the aural intensity with the other three astral.
